        <updateDate>2017-09-11T15:00:32Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Mental Health Access and Gun Violence Prevention Act of </b><b>2017</b></p> <p>This bill authorizes FY2018 appropriations for the Department of Justice, the Department of Health and Human Services, and the Social Security Administration to: (1) increase access to mental health care treatment and services, and (2) promote reporting of mental health information to the National Instant Criminal Background Check System.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
